* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 17:41 Page   1
*                                      EXERC1.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC1.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC1.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION  DIVISION.
     2 PROGRAM-ID.     EXERC1.
     3 AUTHOR.         YHAGO PESSOA.
     4 INSTALLATION.   FATEC-SP.
     5 DATE-WRITTEN.   25/02/2025.
     6 DATE-COMPILED. 18-Mar-25 17:41.
     7 SECURITY. APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICA-LO.
     8*REMARKS.  LE OS REGISTRO DO ARQUIVO DE ENTRADA
     9*          CADCLI1(CODIGO, NOME) E GRAVA NO
    10*          ARQUIVO DE SAIDA CADCLI2 (NOME, CODIGO).
    11
    12 ENVIRONMENT     DIVISION.
    13 CONFIGURATION SECTION.
    14 SOURCE-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    15 OBJECT-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    16 SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    17
    18 INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    19 FILE-CONTROL.
    20     SELECT   CADCLI1      ASSIGN      TO       DISK
    21     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    22     SELECT   CADCLI2        ASSIGN     TO       DISK
    23     ORGANIZATION  IS         LINE        SEQUENTIAL.
    24
    25 DATA           DIVISION.
    26 FILE SECTION.
    27
    28 FD  CADCLI1
    29     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    30     VALUE    OF FILE-ID    IS          "CAD-ENT.DAT".
    31 01  REG-ENT.
    32     02 COD-ENT           PIC 9(05).
    33     02 NOME-ENT          PIC X(20).
    34
    35 FD  CADCLI2
    36     LABEL   RECORD  STANDARD
    37     VALUE   OF FILE-ID    IS   "CAD-SAI.DAT".
    38 01  REG-SAI.
    39     02 NOME-SAI         PIC X(20).
    40     02 COD-SAI          PIC 9(05).
    41 WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    42     77 FIM-ARQ          PIC X(03)    VALUE "NAO".
    43
    44 PROCEDURE        DIVISION.
    45
    46 EXEMPLO.
    47     PERFORM INICIO.
    48     PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    49       UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
    50     PERFORM TERMINO
    51     STOP RUN.
    52 INICIO.
    53     OPEN INPUT CADCLI1
    54          OUTPUT CADCLI2.
    55     PERFORM LEITURA.
    56
    57     LEITURA.
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 17:41 Page   2
*                                      EXERC1.CBL
    58         READ CADCLI1
    59            AT END
    60            MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.
    61 PRINCIPAL.
    62     PERFORM GRAVACAO.
    63     PERFORM LEITURA.
    64
    65     GRAVACAO.
    66         MOVE COD-ENT TO COD-SAI.
    67         MOVE NOME-ENT TO NOME-SAI.
    68         WRITE REG-SAI.
    69
    70 TERMINO.
    71     CLOSE CADCLI1
    72           CADCLI2.
